inStock is an inventory management application for Shopify. You can use inStock to track inventory levels via stock audits, adjust inventory levels with stock adjustments, and receive shipments. inStock will track all data to let you know who did what and when they did it. Sign up for our free 1-month beta period at the <a href="http://apps.shopify.com/shopify_applications/9b8ca7d587384d00267255bfd98cfe65">Shopify App Store</a>. The free beta expires on August 31st.